Source.QueryDefinition:
SELECT * 
FROM [UPDBAccess].[FactLookthroughPositions]
WHERE [UPDBAccess].[FactLookthroughPositions].[PartitionKey] = 20221231
	/*
		AND InvestmentProductKey IN 
			(
				SELECT InvestmentProductKey
				FROM [UPDB].[DimInvestmentProduct]
				WHERE MdmId = 'IP1264'
				   OR MdmParentId = 'IP1264'
			)
	*/

SELECT * 
FROM [UPDBAccess].[FactLookthroughPositions]
WHERE [UPDBAccess].[FactLookthroughPositions].[PartitionKey] = 20230131
	/*
		AND InvestmentProductKey IN 
			(
				SELECT InvestmentProductKey
				FROM [UPDB].[DimInvestmentProduct]
				WHERE MdmId = 'IP1264'
				   OR MdmParentId = 'IP1264'
			)
	*/

SELECT * 
FROM [UPDBAccess].[FactLookthroughPositions]
WHERE [UPDBAccess].[FactLookthroughPositions].[PartitionKey] = 20230228
/*
	AND InvestmentProductKey IN 
		(
			SELECT DISTINCT InvestmentProductKey
			FROM [UPDBAccess].[DimInvestmentProductFlattened]
			WHERE Level_01_MdmId = 'IP3108'
		)
*/

SELECT * 
FROM [UPDBAccess].[FactLookthroughPositions]
WHERE [UPDBAccess].[FactLookthroughPositions].[PartitionKey] = 20230316
	/*
		AND InvestmentProductKey IN 
			(
				SELECT InvestmentProductKey
				FROM [UPDB].[DimInvestmentProduct]
				WHERE MdmId = 'IP1264'
				   OR MdmParentId = 'IP1264'
			)
	*/

SELECT * 
FROM [UPDBAccess].[FactLookthroughPositions]
WHERE [UPDBAccess].[FactLookthroughPositions].[PartitionKey] = 20230317
	/*
		AND InvestmentProductKey IN 
			(
				SELECT InvestmentProductKey
				FROM [UPDB].[DimInvestmentProduct]
				WHERE MdmId = 'IP1264'
				   OR MdmParentId = 'IP1264'
			)
	*/

SELECT * 
FROM [UPDBAccess].[FactLookthroughPositions]
WHERE [UPDBAccess].[FactLookthroughPositions].[PartitionKey] = 20230320
	/*
		AND InvestmentProductKey IN 
			(
				SELECT InvestmentProductKey
				FROM [UPDB].[DimInvestmentProduct]
				WHERE MdmId = 'IP1264'
				   OR MdmParentId = 'IP1264'
			)
	*/

SELECT * 
FROM [UPDBAccess].[FactLookthroughPositions]
WHERE [UPDBAccess].[FactLookthroughPositions].[PartitionKey] = 20230315
	/*
		AND InvestmentProductKey IN

				SELECT InvestmentProductKey
